data.description: Check out this cozy 2-bedroom home just outside of Hibbing! Nestled in a tranquil setting, this property offers the convenience of city water and sewer. Step into the updated kitchen featuring stainless steel appliances, tiled floors, and newer cabinets and countertops, making meal prep a breeze. The bathroom boasts a modern touch with its tiled floor. Plus, you'll love the spacious 2-stall garage, complete with heating via a gas blower, insulation, and electricity, providing ample space for your vehicles and storage needs. With a newer gas forced air furnace/Central Air, you'll have comfort is guaranteed year-round. Newer shingles.
